<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 01:20:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>基于 CTA 的斑块-RADS 评估不明原因栓塞性中风患者非狭窄颈动脉斑块的病因作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cta-based-plaque-rads-to-assess-etiologic-role-of-nonstenotic-carotid-plaques-in-patients-with-embolic-stroke-of-undetermined-source</link><description>背景和目的非狭窄（&amp;lt;50%）颈动脉斑块（NSCP）越来越被认为是不明原因栓塞性卒中（ESUS）的潜在栓塞源，但由于数据有限和缺乏……其病因作用仍不确定。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cta-based-plaque-rads-to-assess-etiologic-role-of-nonstenotic-carotid-plaques-in-patients-with-embolic-stroke-of-undetermined-source2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 01:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cta-based-plaque-rads-to-assess-etiologic-role-of-nonstenotic-carotid-plaques-in-patients-with-embolic-stroke-of-undetermined-source</guid></item><item><title>伟大的Xeelee秘密</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-great-xeelee-secret</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 01:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-great-xeelee-secret</guid></item><item><title>小说中的 10 个类似地狱之星雷米纳的吞噬行星的生命世界</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/10-hellstar-remina-like-planet-eating-living-worlds-in-fiction</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:50:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/10-hellstar-remina-like-planet-eating-living-worlds-in-fiction</guid></item><item><title>数字孪生引导室性心动过速消融</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/digital-twin-guided-ablation-for-ventricular-tachycardia</link><description>在一项 10 名患者的可行性研究中，心脏数字孪生被用来指导 VT 消融。此后，所有患者均无法诱发 VT；平均随访 13 个月，8 名患者未进行药物治疗，未出现复发。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/digital-twin-guided-ablation-for-ventricular-tachycardia.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/digital-twin-guided-ablation-for-ventricular-tachycardia</guid></item><item><title>自 2018 年以来 HRV 持续较高，RHR 较低</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/consistently-higher-hrv-lower-rhr-since-2018</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/consistently-higher-hrv-lower-rhr-since-2018</guid></item><item><title>打开更高效轨道电子设备的大门</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/opening-the-door-to-more-efficient-orbitronic-devices</link><description>电子具有三个固有属性：自旋、电荷和轨道角动量。研究人员长期以来一直在研究如何利用自旋来更有效地产生电流。但轨道电子学领域——基于使用电子的轨道角动量而不是其自旋来产生电流——仍然相对较新。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/opening-the-door-to-more-efficient-orbitronic-devices.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/opening-the-door-to-more-efficient-orbitronic-devices</guid></item><item><title>两人的陪伴：科学家发现了新一类恒星遗迹</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/twos-company-scientists-identify-new-class-of-star-remnants</link><description>在大约 5 到 80 亿年的时间里，我们的太阳预计将演变成一颗白矮星——一种密度极高、地球大小的恒星残骸，它已经耗尽了燃料并脱落了外层。虽然我们的太阳是一颗孤独的恒星，但过去 15 年的研究表明，双星或多星系统比天文学家曾经想象的要普遍得多。当像白矮星这样致密而致密的残余物进入双星系统时，它经常会从伴星上“抢走”物质。这个过程称为吸积，通常会发出 X 射线，被视为“特征”信号。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/twos-company-scientists-identify-new-class-of-star-remnants2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 12:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/twos-company-scientists-identify-new-class-of-star-remnants</guid></item><item><title>MXene 的突破将电导率提高了 160 倍，具有完美的原子序</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/mxene-breakthrough-boosts-conductivity-160x-with-perfect-atomic-order</link><description>一种称为 GLS 方法的新技术采用了一种非常不同的方法。它不依赖刺激性化学品，而是从称为 MAX 相的固体材料开始，并使用熔盐和碘蒸气形成 MXene 片。这个过程使研究人员能够控制哪些卤素原子，包括氯、溴或碘，附着在表面上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mxene-breakthrough-boosts-conductivity-160x-with-perfect-atomic-order.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 12:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/mxene-breakthrough-boosts-conductivity-160x-with-perfect-atomic-order</guid></item><item><title>科学家警告说，流行的维生素 B3 补充剂可能有助于癌细胞生存</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/popular-vitamin-b3-supplements-may-help-cancer-cells-survive-scientists-warn</link><description>一项新的研究对广泛使用的 NAD+ 补充剂提出了重要问题，表明经常服用的用于增强能量和支持健康衰老的化合物可能会在癌症治疗中产生意想不到的后果。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/popular-vitamin-b3-supplements-may-help-cancer-cells-survive-scientists-warn.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 12:02:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/popular-vitamin-b3-supplements-may-help-cancer-cells-survive-scientists-warn</guid></item><item><title>新的遗传工具包可实现全基因组分析</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-genetic-toolkit-enables-genome-wide-analysis</link><description>康奈尔大学的研究人员开发了一种强大的新型遗传工具包，使科学家能够研究基因如何在个体细胞水平上发挥作用，这一进步可能会加速发育、神经科学和疾病方面的发现。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-genetic-toolkit-enables-genome-wide-analysis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 11:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-genetic-toolkit-enables-genome-wide-analysis</guid></item></channel></rss>